    "name": "GitHub Profile Analyzer API",
    "description": "### GitHub Profile Analyzer API\n\nThis Postman collection is configured to test the production-ready REST endpoints of the GitHub Profile Analyzer API.\n\n**Project:** GitHub Profile Analyzer API  \n**Live URL:** [https://github-analyzer-api-1iwr.onrender.com](https://github-analyzer-api-1iwr.onrender.com)  \n\n#### Features:\n- **GitHub Profile Analysis**: Gathers basic profile data and calculates metrics.\n- **Repository Insights**: Extracts total stars, forks, and lists top 5 starred repos.\n- **Engagement Score**: Evaluates user profile engagement mathematically.\n- **Language Breakdown**: Counts programming languages across user public repos.\n- **MySQL Storage**: Persistent, fast cached lookup for analyzed data.\n- **Pagination & Search**: Restricts query outputs, filters results, and sorts by column values.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
